item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: assignment2
item.content:encoded:
Banh Mi Warlocks is a Vietnamese sandwich restaurant. We provide Vietnamese cuisine that consists of a Vietnamese single-serving baguette which call bánh mì. We provide different kind of ingredients from Vietnam.  For example: We use the Vietnamese local meat (beef, chicken, fish, mutton) and homemade sauces. Our goal is to introduce and provide Vietnamese bánh mì to our customers. In addition,  we would like our customer to customize his own unique bánh mì. It can be a full meat bánh mì , vegetarian bánh mì, halal bánh mì and e.t.c.  To save our customers' precious time, we have the Delivery Service between 10:00AM to 7:00PM. We allow our customers make a Pre-Order Reservation between 7:30AM to 11:59PM. If you are surrounding us, you can come to our shop to pick up your meal. ============================================================================ Opening Day: Monday to Friday Opening Time: 8AM To 12AM Rate Us  Notice
